--->Features (Ee project lo unnaavi)
--->Add Task
->Feature:
New task add cheyachu
->Ela use cheyali:
Input box lo type chey (ex: ugra)
Add button click or Enter press
->Result:
Task list lo add avutundi
______________________________
--->Mark as Completed
->Feature:
Task complete ayithe mark cheyachu
->Ela use cheyali:
Task meeda click chey
->Result:
Line strike avutundi (completed)
______________________________
--->Delete Task
->Feature:
Task remove cheyachu
->Ela use cheyali:
Task pakkana X button click chey
->Result:
Task delete avutundi
______________________________
---> Edit Task (Advanced )
->Feature:
Task change cheyachu
->Ela use cheyali:
Task meeda double click chey
Edit chesi Enter pres
->Result:
Task update avutundi
______________________________
--->Filters (All / Active / Completed)
->Feature:
Tasks ni filter cheyachu
->Buttons:
All → anni tasks chupisthayi
Active → incomplete tasks
Completed → completed tasks
______________________________
--->Clear Completed
->Feature:
Completed tasks anni remove chestundi
->Ela use cheyali:
Clear Completed button click
->Result:
Completed tasks delete avuthayi
______________________________
---> Task Counter
->Feature:
Total + completed count chupisthundi
Example:
2/5 completed
_______________________________
--->Local Storage 🔥 (Very Important)
->Feature:
Page refresh ayina tasks delete avvu
Ela work avuthundi:
Browser lo data save chestundi
______________________________
--> Use cheyadam ila:
Task type chey
Add / Enter press
Complete ayithe click chey
Edit kavali ante double click
Delete kavali ante X
Filter use chey
Clear completed use chey
