What is the use of this To-Do List Project?

This project is used to manage and organize daily tasks efficiently.
Simple ga:
“Panulu marchipokunda track cheyadaniki use avuthundi”
________________________________________
Real-Life Uses
 1. Daily Task Management
•	Day lo cheyyali ani tasks list chesukovachu 
•	Example: Study, gym, coding 
________________________________________
 2. Productivity Improve
•	Complete chesina tasks mark cheyadam valla
 motivation periguthundi  
________________________________________
 3. Work Tracking
•	Pending vs completed tasks clear ga kanipistayi 
________________________________________
 4. Personal Planner
•	Small daily planner laga use cheyachu 
________________________________________
 5. Reminder System (basic)
•	Tasks list lo undadam valla marchipokunda untav 
______________________________________________
Technical Uses (important )
 Developer ga:
 1. DOM Manipulation practice
•	Elements add / delete / update 
 2. Event Handling
•	Click, double-click, Enter key 
 3. Local Storage
•	Data browser lo save cheyadam 
 4. UI Design
•	Clean interface build cheyadam 
 5. Logic Building
•	Real-world problem solve cheyadam

